<p>When your tree is finished, send a photo. Then explain what you did with these sentence starters — write 4 sentences.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>First, I built the trunk by placing brown blocks at …</p>
<p>The lowest block in my picture is at (x = …, y = …).</p>
<p>To go across a row I changed the … number; to go up I changed the … number.</p>
<p>The trickiest part to read off the grid was …</p>
</blockquote>
